data.title: 4690 STROUSE SONGS OF CHARLES STROU
data.meta_description: Charles Strouse has composed the scores to some of Broadway's most successful and enduring musicals – including Annie, Applause and Bye Bye Birdie – as well as many memorable TV themes. Our revised folio honors this Tony and Emmy winner with PVG arrangements of 50 wonderful songs: Applause • Born Too Late • It's the Ha
